EXPO_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_ACCESS_TOKEN=pk.ey...
# Cognito (email/password + Hosted UI for Apple/Google)
# EXPO_PUBLIC_COGNITO_USER_POOL_ID=us-east-1_xxxxx
# EXPO_PUBLIC_COGNITO_CLIENT_ID=xxxxx
# For Hosted UI: Cognito domain (NOT cognito-idp...amazonaws.com). Example:
# https://your-prefix.auth.us-east-2.amazoncognito.com
# EXPO_PUBLIC_COGNITO_OAUTH_DOMAIN=https://your-prefix.auth.us-east-2.amazoncognito.com
# Optional: space-separated OAuth scopes (must match Cognito app client "Allowed OAuth scopes").
# Default is openid. Add email profile when enabled in AWS, e.g.:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_COGNITO_OAUTH_SCOPES=openid email profile